item.title: CVE-2023-0420|2023-04-24T18:30:49.071Z -- unknown -- custom%20post%20type%20and%20taxonomy%20gui%20manager
item.description: The Custom Post Type and Taxonomy GUI Manager WordPress plugin through 1.1 does not have CSRF, and is lacking sanitising as well as escaping in some parameters, allowing attackers to make a logged in admin put Stored Cross-Site Scripting payloads via CSRF
